				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$(\mathrm{Da}_\mathrm{vap})$$\end{document} used in this study is defined as the ratio of volatilization time (τvap)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
