				\begin{document}$$(\tau _\mathrm{vap})$$\end{document} to characteristic reaction time (τchem)\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym}
				\usepackage{amsfonts}
